{"id":"features/grid/empty-collection-template","title":"Empty Collection Template","contents":"<h1 id=\"empty-collection-template\"><a href=\"#empty-collection-template\" aria-hidden><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Empty collection template</h1>\n<p>When the datasource does not contain items (length is 0) the table will show the empty collection template.</p>\n<p>The template can be defined at any location using the structural directive <strong><code class=\"language-text\">*pblNgridNoDataRef</code></strong></p>\n<div><div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">*pblNgridNoDataRef</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>pbl-ngrid-no-data<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>No Results<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div></div>\n<blockquote class=\"info icon\">\n<div class=\"icon-location\"></div>\n The Empty Collection Template is part of the registry, i.e. - Registry cascading rules apply.\n</blockquote>\n<div pbl-example-view=\"pbl-empty-collection-template-example\"></div>\n<div pbl-example-view=\"pbl-asynchronous-empty-set-example\"></div>\n<div pbl-example-view=\"pbl-dynamic-set-example\"></div>\n"}